                  , about the hour of eight in the night of the <rs id="t17960217-49-cd278" type="crimeDate">25th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960217-49-off277 t17960217-49-cd278"></join>, and burglariously stealing 3 pieces of printed calico, containing 15 yards, value 40s. the property of the said 
