                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960217-49-defend496 t17960217-49-punish282"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice LAWRENCE.</p>
